    "(2) The gap between the GPT-4 and other models: Although ToM capability improves nearly all models, GPT-4 consistently outperforms other LLMs.",
    "This superiority is particularly evident when the agents are pitted against the three baselines.",
    "In these matchups, the agent based on GPT-4 achieves an impressive average score of +2.17, demonstrating its exceptional skills in the Guandan card game.",
    "In contrast, the best performance among the other LLMs reaches only +1.36, a notable difference of 0.81 points compared to GPT-4.",
    "This disparity in performance can be attributed to GPT-4's advanced ability to leverage ToM knowledge better and make more strategic decisions in the complex environment of Guandan."
